that cannot be cured easily.

580
00:43:52,875 --> 00:43:54,750
So, Princess Sabrina must be sad?

581
00:43:55,208 --> 00:43:56,208
Yes.

582
00:43:58,375 --> 00:44:01,666
If it turns out

583
00:44:03,458 --> 00:44:07,375
