631
00:48:37,500 --> 00:48:38,500
Arini!

632
00:48:39,041 --> 00:48:40,166
Where is the key?

633
00:48:40,250 --> 00:48:41,500
Where are you going?

634
00:48:43,333 --> 00:48:46,250
