636
00:48:55,333 --> 00:48:56,833
You are Nadia's mother.

637
00:49:03,208 --> 00:49:05,375
Sheila, stop worrying.

638
00:49:05,458 --> 00:49:07,458
Don't be scared, okay?

639
00:49:11,375 --> 00:49:13,000
I just want

640
00:49:14,791 --> 00:49:17,125
