649
00:49:50,500 --> 00:49:53,708
Szentendre, to meet Aunt Mei.

650
00:49:57,958 --> 00:50:00,916
I need to watch over you two.

651
00:50:01,000 --> 00:50:03,208
Let Panji pick up Pras from the airport.

652
