679
00:51:14,208 --> 00:51:15,375
Oh, my God!
What is this?

680
00:51:16,708 --> 00:51:18,958
Sandwich filled with love.

681
00:51:19,416 --> 00:51:20,416
Akbar.

682
00:51:20,958 --> 00:51:22,500
