708
00:54:20,958 --> 00:54:22,166
-Arini?
-Yes?

709
00:54:24,708 --> 00:54:26,541
You look a bit pale.

710
00:54:29,958 --> 00:54:32,833
I'm just tired, Mei.

711
00:54:32,916 --> 00:54:35,625
