898
01:07:09,875 --> 01:07:12,500
Please go with Mei, honey.

899
01:07:12,583 --> 01:07:13,583
Give her a ride, hon.

900
01:07:13,666 --> 01:07:14,666
You see that?

901
01:07:14,750 --> 01:07:17,333
