1067
01:19:34,666 --> 01:19:36,583
Can he use the chili ointment?

1068
01:19:40,250 --> 01:19:42,041
Poor Amran.

1069
01:19:42,125 --> 01:19:43,708
It's his own fault.

1070
01:19:43,791 --> 01:19:46,083
