1088
01:20:49,250 --> 01:20:51,500
So, strong women exist.

1089
01:20:58,333 --> 01:20:59,333
Arini.

1090
01:20:59,958 --> 01:21:01,000
-George.
-Arini.

1091
01:21:03,583 --> 01:21:05,041
Hi. Hello.

1092
01:21:19,791 --> 01:21:23,458
