1093
01:21:46,416 --> 01:21:47,500
Arini?

1094
01:21:53,375 --> 01:21:54,375
Arini!

1095
01:21:57,208 --> 01:21:58,625
Sorry, I'll call you back.

1096
01:22:41,041 --> 01:22:43,875
