1102
01:23:16,500 --> 01:23:17,500
No.

1103
01:23:20,000 --> 01:23:21,125
No, honey.

1104
01:23:21,750 --> 01:23:23,500
We can still try.

1105
01:23:25,333 --> 01:23:26,333
Enough.

1106
01:23:50,541 --> 01:23:51,541
Pras.

1107
01:23:56,958 --> 01:24:00,541
