1137
01:26:44,708 --> 01:26:45,708
Oh, God.

1138
01:26:47,958 --> 01:26:49,416
Oh, God.

1139
01:26:55,333 --> 01:26:56,583
Sorry, Doc.

1140
01:26:57,416 --> 01:26:58,750
It's okay.

1141
01:27:06,708 --> 01:27:07,708
I...

