1228
01:35:37,541 --> 01:35:39,583
I will still look to you for guidance.

1229
01:36:43,416 --> 01:36:44,416
Mei?

1230
01:36:48,416 --> 01:36:49,708
Sorry, Mei.

1231
01:36:50,208 --> 01:36:51,375
I didn't

