01:38:17,916 --> 01:38:18,916
Arini?

1252
01:38:19,750 --> 01:38:21,291
Doctor Syarief.

1253
01:38:21,833 --> 01:38:23,458
You know him?

1254
01:38:23,541 --> 01:38:24,541
-She...
-Yes.

1255
01:38:24,625 --> 01:38:26,291
