all of Nadia's needs.

1290
01:41:41,166 --> 01:41:44,625
I will try to make you happy.

1291
01:41:49,791 --> 01:41:50,791
Honey?

1292
01:41:53,041 --> 01:41:54,041
Honey?

1293
01:41:55,166 --> 01:41:56,166
Arini?

1294
01:43:04,041 --> 01:43:07,250
